## 基础信息：
gitlab版本：gitlab-ce:12.6.2
gitlab ssh 端口：12222
gitlab-mirror：https://github.com/samrocketman/gitlab-mirrors.git


## 准备工作
新建gitmirror用户，生成ssh key
```bash
adduser gitmirror
su - gitmirror
ssh-keygen
more ~/.ssh/id_rsa.pub
```

公钥复制到两台gitlab配置免密登录，免密测试
```bash
ssh -T git@xxx.xxx.xxx.xx -p 12222
Welcome to GitLab, @username!
```

在~/.ssh目录下创建config文件：
```bash
Host "xxx.xxx.xxx.xx"
Port "12222"
```
"xxx.xxx.xxx.xx" 是gitlab mirror服务器ip

设置private_token调用gitlab api

![gitlab][gitlab]
```bash
touch ~/private_token
echo 'xxxxxxxxxx' > ~/private_token
```

安装python-gitlab类库
```bash
yum install -y python-pip
pip install python-gitlab
```

## gitlab-mirror配置修改
config.sh
```bash
# gitmirror 所运行的用户
system_user="gitmirror"
# gitlab mirror 上的 group，需要提前创建
gitlab_namespace="deploy"
# gitlab mirror ip
gitlab_url="http://xxx.xxx.xxx.xx"
# gitlab mirror 管理员账户
gitlab_user="root"
# ssl证书验证
ssl_verify=false
```

gitmirror用户根目录下创建repostories目录
```bash
# gitlab-mirror将代码clone到本地的默认路径
mkdir -p ~/repostories
```

同步仓库
```bash
~/gitlab-mirror/add_mirror.sh --git --project-name integration --mirror git@xxx.xxx.xxx.xx:deploy/integration.git
# cron 定时同步
*/1 * * * * /home/gitmirror/gitlab-mirrors/git-mirrors.sh
```
